title: Index of Factory Payrolls, Food Products for United States
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1919-1942 (2)--Original Data, 1947-1954. Source: For Data Through 1934, Bureau Of Labor Statistics Mimeographed Release, September, 1938, Pp.49, 50, 31, 32, 55; For 1935-39 Data, Bureau Of Labor Statistics Mimeographed Release, May, 1940; Thereafter, "Employment And Payrolls" And Monthly Labor Review.
